### Notifications API - Test Endpoints

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@contentType = application/json

### Root - Redirige a Swagger
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### API Info
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/info

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Health Check Ready
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/ready

### Health Check Detailed
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/detailed

### Send Notification - Success (201)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/send
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "usuarioId": "a1b2c3d4-0000-0000-0000-111122223333",
  "mensaje": "Su orden #f1e2d3c4 fue confirmada.",
  "tipo": "Email"
}

### Send Notification - User Not Found (404 - NTF-001)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/send
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "usuarioId": "invalid-user-id",
  "mensaje": "Test notification",
  "tipo": "Email"
}

### Send Notification - Invalid Data (400 - NTF-002)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/send
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "usuarioId": "",
  "mensaje": "Test",
  "tipo": "Email"
}

### Send Notification - Missing Fields (400 - NTF-002)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/send
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "usuarioId": "a1b2c3d4-0000-0000-0000-111122223333"
}

### Get Notifications by User - Success (200)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/a1b2c3d4-0000-0000-0000-111122223333

### Get Notifications by User - User Not Found (404 - NTF-001)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/invalid-user-id

### Get Notifications by User - No Notifications Found (404 - NTF-003)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/different-user-id

### With Custom Correlation ID
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/send
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
X-Correlation-Id: my-custom-correlation-123

{
  "usuarioId": "a1b2c3d4-0000-0000-0000-111122223333",
  "mensaje": "Test con Correlation ID",
  "tipo": "SMS"
}
